reviews.review_text: High energy recording of a very well played show by the Dead... great sounding aud recording. Great sounding drums & cymbals by Billy & Mickey, Brett's organ nice & clean, and Jerry is on fire. captures Phil better than most if not all of the other recordings offered for this show.Top shelf playing by everyone. Fantastic Cumberland, Cassidy, Railroad, All over now, Estimated, Terrapin, Eyes, Good Lovin. Bobby's singing is on fire. Just a top shelf show by the band ...and the audience sounds like they had a blast!  Be nice if Dead/Rhino puts out a box of the 6 shows performed at Merriweather Post Pavilion from 83-85. really really stellar playing.
